# Loadout Inventory App Database

This app uses Supabase (PostgreSQL) as its database. All app data is stored persistently including:
- Item inventory with photos
- Stock transactions (add, use, adjust)
- Suppliers and preferences
- Jobs and job parts
- Tools and tool checkouts
- Saved report views
- Feature toggle settings
- Share/email logs

Set the DATABASE_URL and DIRECT_URL environment variables (see .env.example) to connect.
